{"tid":1220281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[建議]不如分返時事政事台","createTime":"2019-06-14T03:32:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T07:21:10.000Z","uid":44925,"like":26,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6aeb96374d577db80d5a65917f7bcee005f31ce8","tid":1220281,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:32:23.000Z","msg":"大家好 麻煩大家如果開po前請睇一睇<br />\n近幾日資訊實在爆棚 大家有唔同消息都急不及待Share 而且各位巴絲有好多好好既建議想分享<br />\n<br />\n但係我發覺好多有用既資訊其實沉左底<br />\n<br />\n所以我有一個建議<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">關於策略開係政事台</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">關於即時資訊開返係時事台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n盡量俾有用既post多人睇到 唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7a79b12dea92a62b2c532f37332d5886f1b7913","tid":1220281,"uid":44925,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"所謂內幕消息<br />\n唔好推唔好理"},{"pid":"b59d00dd5958cac415bdb77a8487be19cbc86346","tid":1220281,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"咁都有人負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f1d417d5f28bc6fb027639b9f20e3d99b90d05","tid":1220281,"uid":44925,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e7a79b12dea92a62b2c532f37332d5886f1b7913","tid":1220281,"uid":44925,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:33:32.000Z","msg":"所謂內幕消息<br />\n唔好推唔好理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"咩內幕消息<br />\n咩我男朋友係咩 女朋友係咩<br />\n<br />\n負皮 上一頁"},{"pid":"b74ca0f70e0611f23ae6212ae997c453ce7c0f61","tid":1220281,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以叫連仔好似bam或者fiter劇頭post咁搞曬d內幕消息post架，真係好煩，d人呢個時候都仲有心情出膠post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d17e5bb6f39e8c7e4f1c6bc7b126cdd9cff032","tid":1220281,"uid":256246,"li